{"tid":2054903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【中伏飲食】觀塘連鎖餐廳凍檸茶「加料」大曱甴　港男：咁大個仔第一次遇到","createTime":"2020-06-07T13:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:46:38.000Z","uid":208710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1dcf47c8900d7f4464c7a995b65881dfe4fe677","tid":2054903,"uid":208710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2660000/2663750/lemontea_thumb_20200607_D_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2660000%2F2663750%2Flemontea_thumb_20200607_D_1024.jpg&h=e7603a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外出用餐最講究餐廳的乾淨程度，有網民分享自己的中伏經歷，他在觀塘光顧了一間連鎖的西式餐廳，並點了一杯凍檸檬茶，豈料凍檸檬茶中漂浮一隻超大隻曱甴，令他大感嘔心，立即離開。<br />\n<br />\n該名網民今日（7日）在「中伏飲食報料區」發帖，分享了自己的中伏遭遇，他上傳了一張相片及一條短片，並留言指<br />\n<br />\n成世人咁大個仔第一次遇到成隻曱甴浸落杯凍檸茶比人飲，即走唔食！<br />\n<br />\n從相片可見，涉事的凍檸茶中，明顯可以見到一隻曱甴浸在中間。該名網民又拍攝短片，並將曱甴撈出來，清晰見到曱甴相當大隻。<br />\n<br />\n帖子引起網民熱論紛紛，有網民形容如此大隻曱甴相當令人嘔心，並指曱甴浸在凍檸茶中，好似「浸藥酒」。也有人估計，檸檬茶所用的檸檬，可以提早已經放入杯子中，估計曱甴爬入杯子偷食檸檬而不被人發現。<br />\n<br />\n也有網民對餐廳的衛生感到失望，指如此大隻曱甴，即使負責酒吧的職員察覺唔到，負責上菜的職員為何都沒有察覺到，更留言指涉事網民很好彩，因為幸好沒有飲用，如果戳了檸檬再飲，相信涉事網民可能要洗胃。"},{"pid":"61420d4b5e5bdec68d016cef37e96d19068e7915","tid":2054903,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"幾間，開名"},{"pid":"6ca3a3413d9e85f1a8795e609c5c4f68086cff15","tid":2054903,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61420d4b5e5bdec68d016cef37e96d19068e7915","tid":2054903,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"幾間，開名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dbe6dae98c51eee701a02b320a8876c2e699c0","tid":2054903,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"收你跟餐幾蚊杯野飲, <br />\n呢d 意外屋企沖都會發生啦<br />\n好心唔好搞到人揾唔到食咁肉酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f768df3051625d5c60f68c2ca8c36c4ddab39aac","tid":2054903,"uid":121233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"已經唔加收你錢<br />\n仲想點"},{"pid":"4ceb83d25e75120123c6c6db09ca43ff15c0e8c4","tid":2054903,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"3萬thx"},{"pid":"70b1fe9e8742b99a0460981d2d696381c34e4335","tid":2054903,"uid":281483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"藍店花園餐廳係咁上下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}